author: adrianc
msg: Moved JobInvoker.java code to AbstractJob.java, removed JobInvoker.java. Also worked on the Job API - the meaning of "runtime" was a little muddled, so I made "runtime" mean job execution elapsed time, and added a getStartTime method to the Job interface. This should make the distinction clearer.
This commit completes the Job Scheduler overhaul.
